## Design System

### Philosophy
Clean, functional, and fast. The driver app is used in the field — no decorative flourishes. The back office is a data tool — clarity over style. Mazati brand colours appear as accents only, not as backgrounds or dominant colours.

### Colour System

**Brand Accent:**
- Mazati Green `#51836D` — primary CTAs, active states, badges, key highlights only
- Use sparingly — one or two elements per view maximum

**Backgrounds:**
- Page background: `bg-gray-50`
- Card/panel background: `bg-white`
- Input background: `bg-white`

**Text:**
- Primary: `text-gray-900`
- Secondary: `text-gray-600`
- Muted/hint: `text-gray-400`
- On Mazati Green background: `text-white`

**Borders:**
- Default: `border-gray-200`
- Focus ring: `ring-[#51836D]`

**Functional Colours:**
- Success: `bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700 border-emerald-200`
- Warning: `bg-amber-50 text-amber-700 border-amber-200`
- Danger: `bg-red-50 text-red-700 border-red-200`
- Info: `bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 border-blue-200`

**Delivery Status Colours:**
| Status | Classes |
|---|---|
| pending | `bg-gray-100 text-gray-600` |
| assigned | `bg-blue-100 text-blue-700` |
| in_transit | `bg-amber-100 text-amber-700` |
| completed | `bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700` |
| attempted | `bg-orange-100 text-orange-700` |

### Buttons
```tsx
// Primary — use Mazati green inline style (not a Tailwind class)
<button style={{ backgroundColor: '#51836D' }} className="text-white rounded-lg px-4 py-2 hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">
  Confirm Delivery
</button>

// Secondary
<button className="border border-gray-300 text-gray-700 rounded-lg px-4 py-2 hover:bg-gray-50">
  Cancel
</button>

// Destructive
<button className="bg-red-600 text-white rounded-lg px-4 py-2 hover:bg-red-700">
  Delete
</button>

// Driver app — large touch target variant
<button style={{ backgroundColor: '#51836D' }} className="text-white rounded-xl px-6 py-4 text-base font-medium w-full hover:opacity-90 active:opacity-80">
  Submit POD
</button>
```

### shadcn/ui Usage
- Use shadcn components from `components/ui` for all standard UI elements
- Style: New York, Base: Slate, CSS variables: Yes
- Override with `className` to match the Mazati brand colour where needed

### Layout & Spacing
- Back office page container: `max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-8`
- Card pattern: `bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6`
- Section gaps: `gap-6`
- Card padding: `p-6`

### Typography
- Page title: `text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900`
- Section title: `text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900`
- Card title: `text-base font-semibold text-gray-900`
- Body: `text-sm text-gray-600`
- Muted: `text-sm text-gray-400`

### Icons
- Lucide React exclusively
- Standard size: `w-5 h-5`
- In buttons: `w-4 h-4`
- Always set explicit colour — never rely on inheritance

### Responsive Design
- **Back office primary**: Desktop (1024px+)
- **Back office secondary**: Tablet (768px+)
- **Driver app primary**: Mobile (375px+)
- **Driver app secondary**: iPad (768px+)

